name: Sensor Web Server Helgoland API v3.2.0
body:
Available in [Maven Central](https://search.maven.org/search?q=g:org.n52.sensorweb-server.helgoland%20and%20v:3.2.0).

## Change Log 

* Fix lgtm issue with HTTP response splitting (#502)
* Update junit tests to junit 5
* Fix some tests

### Dependency Updates

* Bump arctic-sea.version from 7.4.0 to 7.4.1 (#503)
* Update geotools from 22.3 to 23.0
* Bump version.junit from 5.6.1 to 5.6.2 (#504)
* Bump spotbugs-annotations from 4.0.1 to 4.0.2 (#505 )
* Bump jackson-annotations from 2.10.3 to 2.11.0 (#506 )
* Bump spotbugs-annotations from 4.0.2 to 4.0.3 (#508 )
* Bump fop-core from 2.4 to 2.5 (#509 )
* Bump spring-boot-dependencies from 2.2.7.RELEASE to 2.3.0.RELEASE (#510 )
* Update spring from 5.2.1 to 5.2.6
* Bump commons-io from 2.6 to 2.7 (#511)
* Update arctic-sea version from 7.4.1 to 7.5.0

### Breaking Changes

See [here](https://github.com/52North/sensorweb-server-helgoland/compare/v3.1.0...v3.2.0) for the complete commit log.
